  "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/5597",
  "title": "Pagination link hrefs not consistent server and client side",
  "body": "### 🐛 Current behavior\n\nWhen rendering the <Pagination /> component server-side the URLs in the href attribute do not include the relevant query parameters for pagination. When hydrated client-side they do.\r\n\r\nI am using the `react-instantsearch-hooks-router-nextjs` library with a custom route state object and `createURL` function. \r\n\r\nServer rendered code:\r\n```html\r\n      <div class=\"pagination\">\r\n            <div class=\"ais-Pagination\">\r\n              <ul class=\"ais-Pagination-list\">\r\n                <li\r\n                  class=\"ais-Pagination-item ais-Pagination-item--disabled ais-Pagination-item--firstPage\">\r\n                  <span class=\"ais-Pagination-link\" aria-label=\"First\">‹‹</span>\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li\r\n                  class=\"ais-Pagination-item ais-Pagination-item--disabled ais-Pagination-item--previousPage\">\r\n                  <span class=\"ais-Pagination-link\" aria-label=\"Previous\">‹</span>\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li\r\n                  class=\"ais-Pagination-item ais-Pagination-item--page ais-Pagination-item--selected\">\r\n                  <a class=\"ais-Pagination-link\" href=\"/\" aria-label=\"Page 1\">1</a>\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li class=\"ais-Pagination-item ais-Pagination-item--page\"><a\r\n                    class=\"ais-Pagination-link\" href=\"/\" aria-label=\"Page 2\">2</a></li>\r\n                <li class=\"ais-Pagination-item ais-Pagination-item--page\"><a\r\n                    class=\"ais-Pagination-link\" href=\"/\" aria-label=\"Page 3\">3</a></li>\r\n                <li class=\"ais-Pagination-item ais-Pagination-item--page\"><a\r\n                    class=\"ais-Pagination-link\" href=\"/\" aria-label=\"Page 4\">4</a></li>\r\n                <li class=\"ais-Pagination-item ais-Pagination-item--page\"><a\r\n                    class=\"ais-Pagination-link\" href=\"/\" aria-label=\"Page 5\">5</a></li>\r\n                <li class=\"ais-Pagination-item ais-Pagination-item--page\"><a\r\n                    class=\"ais-Pagination-link\" href=\"/\" aria-label=\"Page 6\">6</a></li>\r\n                <li class=\"ais-Pagination-item ais-Pagination-item--page\"><a\r\n                    class=\"ais-Pagination-link\" href=\"/\" aria-label=\"Page 7\">7</a></li>\r\n                <li class=\"ais-Pagination-item ais-Pagination-item--nextPage\"><a\r\n                    class=\"ais-Pagination-link\" href=\"/\" aria-label=\"Next\">›</a></li>\r\n                <li class=\"ais-Pagination-item ais-Pagination-item--lastPage\"><a\r\n                    class=\"ais-Pagination-link\" href=\"/\" aria-label=\"Last\">››</a></li>\r\n              </ul>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n```\r\n\r\nClient-rendered:\r\n```html\r\n          <div class=\"pagination\">\r\n            <div class=\"ais-Pagination\">\r\n              <ul class=\"ais-Pagination-list\">\r\n                <li\r\n                  class=\"ais-Pagination-item ais-Pagination-item--disabled ais-Pagination-item--firstPage\">\r\n                  <span class=\"ais-Pagination-link\" aria-label=\"First\">‹‹</span>\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li\r\n                  class=\"ais-Pagination-item ais-Pagination-item--disabled ais-Pagination-item--previousPage\">\r\n                  <span class=\"ais-Pagination-link\" aria-label=\"Previous\">‹</span>\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li\r\n                  class=\"ais-Pagination-item ais-Pagination-item--page ais-Pagination-item--selected\">\r\n                  <a class=\"ais-Pagination-link\" href=\"/\" aria-label=\"Page 1\">1</a></li>\r\n                <li class=\"ais-Pagination-item ais-Pagination-item--page\"><a\r\n                    class=\"ais-Pagination-link\" href=\"/?p_page=2\" aria-label=\"Page 2\">2</a></li>\r\n                <li class=\"ais-Pagination-item ais-Pagination-item--page\"><a\r\n                    class=\"ais-Pagination-link\" href=\"/?p_page=3\" aria-label=\"Page 3\">3</a></li>\r\n                <li class=\"ais-Pagination-item ais-Pagination-item--page\"><a\r\n                    class=\"ais-Pagination-link\" href=\"/?p_page=4\" aria-label=\"Page 4\">4</a></li>\r\n                <li class=\"ais-Pagination-item ais-Pagination-item--page\"><a\r\n                    class=\"ais-Pagination-link\" href=\"/?p_page=5\" aria-label=\"Page 5\">5</a></li>\r\n                <li class=\"ais-Pagination-item ais-Pagination-item--page\"><a\r\n                    class=\"ais-Pagination-link\" href=\"/?p_page=6\" aria-label=\"Page 6\">6</a></li>\r\n                <li class=\"ais-Pagination-item ais-Pagination-item--page\"><a\r\n                    class=\"ais-Pagination-link\" href=\"/?p_page=7\" aria-label=\"Page 7\">7</a></li>\r\n                <li class=\"ais-Pagination-item ais-Pagination-item--nextPage\"><a\r\n                    class=\"ais-Pagination-link\" href=\"/?p_page=2\" aria-label=\"Next\">›</a></li>\r\n                <li class=\"ais-Pagination-item ais-Pagination-item--lastPage\"><a\r\n                    class=\"ais-Pagination-link\" href=\"/?p_page=125\" aria-label=\"Last\">››</a></li>\r\n              </ul>\r\n            </div>\r\n          </div>\r\n```\n\n### 🔍 Steps to reproduce\n\n1. Implement Next.js SSR with `react-instantsearch-hooks-router-nextjs`\r\n2. Deploy <Pagination />\r\n3. Use a custom createURL function\n\n### Live reproduction\n\nhttps://github.com/richardweaver/algolia-pagination-ssr-issue\n\n### 💭 Expected behavior\n\n<Pagination /> should render identically on server- and client-side.\n\n### Package version\n\nreact-instantsearch-hooks-server / react-instantsearch-hooks-web / react-instantsearch-hooks-router-nextjs 6.42.2\n\n### Operating system\n\nmacOS 13.3.1\n\n### Browser\n\nChrome 112.0.5615.49\n\n### Code of Conduct\n\n- [X] I agree to follow this project's Code of Conduct",
